# comment-special-chars

## Input

```
# { } | > "hello" 'world'
key value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..36
  COMMENT@0..25
    SHARP@0..1 "#"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    CLOSE_BRACE@4..5 "}"
    SPACE@5..6 " "
    PIPE@6..7 "|"
    SPACE@7..8 " "
    GT@8..9 ">"
    SPACE@9..10 " "
    DOUBLE_QUOTE@10..11 "\""
    STRING@11..16 "hello"
    DOUBLE_QUOTE@16..17 "\""
    SPACE@17..18 " "
    SINGLE_QUOTE@18..19 "'"
    STRING@19..24 "world"
    SINGLE_QUOTE@24..25 "'"
  NEWLINE@25..26 "\n"
  ENTRY@26..36
    WORD_KEY@26..29
      WORD@26..29 "key"
    SPACE@29..30 " "
    LINE_STRING@30..35
      STRING@30..35 "value"
    NEWLINE@35..36 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@26..29 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@30..35 "value",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

